Package cz.cuni.mff.mozharon.financialaccounting.application.config

Class ServiceConfig

java.lang.Object
cz.cuni.mff.mozharon.financialaccounting.application.config.ServiceConfig
public class ServiceConfig extends Object
Configuration class for service layer dependencies. This class handles the construction and dependency injection of service layer components.
